CPInterfaceMethodEntry
public class CPMethodEntry
extends CPEntry

Constant pool entry for methods. In a first pass read the class_index and name_and_type_index in the constant pool being constructed. In a second pass after the entire constant pool has been constructed resolve the indices to actual names and descriptors. File created June 12, 2000
